title: Action Comics 23.2 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Action Comics 23.2 (Zod)

By:   	Greg Pak, Ken Lashley, Gene Ha	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Publisher:   	DC Comics	
Pub. Date:  	September 11, 2013
Format:         CBZ

General Zod storms into The New 52!

Witness the origin of this genocidal maniac, and learn how far he will go to destroy those who oppose him!
